OL,3,CJohn Stones and Noni Madueke start as
OL,4,CEngland fans gather for Norway match
OL,6,FJohn Stones and Noni Madueke came into
OL,7,Fthe England team as Thomas Tuchel made
OL,8,Ftwo changes for the World Cup quarter-
OL,9,Ffinal with Norway.
OL,11,FStones, who recently left Manchester
OL,12,FCity as a free agent, will play
OL,13,Fcentral defence alongside Marc Guehi,
OL,14,Fwho has shaken off a hamstring injury,
OL,15,Fwith the duo putting club allegiances
OL,16,Fto one side as they try to keep City's
OL,17,FErling Haaland quiet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
