OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783873241
OL,3,CJohn Stones and Noni Madueke start as
OL,4,CEngland fans gather for Norway match
OL,6,FEzri Konsa shifts over to right-back
OL,7,Fas he did in the last-16 win against
OL,8,FMexico following the red card to
OL,9,FJarell Quansah, who begins a two-match
OL,10,Fban.
OL,12,FReece James has been recovering from a
OL,13,Fhamstring injury, but he is not deemed
OL,14,Ffit enough to start.
OL,16,FMadueke returns to the team in place
OL,17,Fof Arsenal team-mate Bukayo Saka, who
OL,18,Fis still managing an Achilles injury.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
