OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783873241
OL,3,CJohn Stones and Noni Madueke start as
OL,4,CEngland fans gather for Norway match
OL,6,FWhen Kane was asked who is the better
OL,7,Fahead of the match, he replied: "It is
OL,8,Fan impossible one for me to answer.
OL,10,F"First of all, I think we are
OL,11,Fcompletely different players almost. I
OL,12,Fknow we are both seen as strikers, but
OL,13,Fit is almost two different positions
OL,14,Fif I'm totally honest.
OL,16,F"Erling has been incredible, his
OL,17,Fgoalscoring record. Physically, he's a
OL,18,Fmachine, he's a beast. His finishing
OL,19,Fis at the highest level and obviously
OL,20,Fhis goalscoring record speaks for
OL,21,Fitself.
OL,26,@oD@aOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
