OL,3,CJohn Stones and Noni Madueke start as
OL,4,CEngland fans gather for Norway match
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"I see myself as a different player
OL,12,Falthough I score the same goals. I
OL,13,Flike to maybe touch the ball a little
OL,14,Fbit more, be involved in play a little
OL,15,Fbit more but also can play as an out-
OL,16,Fand-out nine.
