PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783873241
OL,3,CJohn Stones and Noni Madueke start as
OL,4,CEngland fans gather for Norway match
OL,6,FThis hasn't stopped England fans
OL,7,Fturning out in droves for the game
OL,8,Fwith many turning up hours before kick
OL,9,Foff to get their seats for the match.
OL,11,FIf England win the game, they will
OL,12,Fface either Argentina or Switzerland
OL,13,Fin the semi-final.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
